{"tid":2490757,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大學生杯葛：費事俾個制度玩","createTime":"2021-04-16T00:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T05:42:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1acbb1070ec6ffe566a039a543530da9e83c0f4c","tid":2490757,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T00:15:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/WXYX2APHPVEHLNT4DPJ7CWEOUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FWXYX2APHPVEHLNT4DPJ7CWEOUI%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwFScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=21517863\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FWXYX2APHPVEHLNT4DPJ7CWEOUI%2F&h=5cc2adf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/WXYX2APHPVEHLNT4DPJ7CWEOUI/</a><br />\n<br />\n大學生杯葛：費事俾個制度玩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9UB0ExSmzsY60df1cwqHVfUIgyQ=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ELPJHSZSFVHZ7EEOUV3RSHBSM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9UB0ExSmzsY60df1cwqHVfUIgyQ%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FELPJHSZSFVHZ7EEOUV3RSHBSM4.jpg&h=6b6e94c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大學生陳小姐傾向不投票，認為議會已無法監察政府。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特區政府操刀大改香港選舉制度，大幅削減民主成份之餘，更加入任何人「煽惑」他人不投票、投白票或廢票，即干犯刑事罪，最高可被判監三年。本報於街頭訪問部份選民，不少人表示個人傾向杯葛未來選舉。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「沙田三八線」左右出口不同區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n質疑「真民主派」能否入閘<br />\n<br />\n過去多數票投本土派的醫護人員葉小姐直言，打算杯葛未來所有選舉，批評選舉制度經港府閹割後，候選人要經掌權者篩選，「根本就係政府揀一啲人畀我揀，DQ一啲市民真正想選擇的人」，又指參與民主派初選人士因涉觸犯國安法被捕，「呢啲人已經冇得再參選」，即使有同一理念「新血」出選，入閘機會亦不大，「反正個選舉都咁不公，我再投票都冇意思。」<br />\n<br />\n大學生陳小姐亦傾向不投票，認為議會已無法監察政府，「就算選到入到去，都做唔到啲咩，好似俾個制度玩緊咁。」對於政府擬規管呼籲人不投票、投白票等，陳小姐直斥政府「癲咗囉好似」，認為投票屬選民自由，「討論吓都要死咁，焗你一定要做某啲事，講吓都唔得。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：曾蔭權、梁振英曾「煽惑」不投票<br />\n<br />\n不過亦有部份選民持觀望態度。從事會計行業黎先生以往多數票投民主派，會否再投票視乎候選人名單，「要睇吓揀唔揀到啦，揀唔到，就睇吓有咩方法反映到民意囉⋯⋯你明我明咪得，哈哈」，但他亦質疑「真民主派」能否入閘參選。<br />\n<br />\n大學生黎小姐亦表示，視乎有哪些候選人入閘，再決定未來是否投票，若有非建制派人士參選，會盡選民責任。對於政府進一步要求市民在選舉中噤聲，她直言不感到意外，但不會因此變得政治冷感。<br />\n<br />\n自由工作者葉小姐則表示會投票，「點樣投，係咪喺上面寫啲嘢就另一回事，不過就梗係唔好投白票啦」，又批評政府改革選舉制度「咁大件事，冇諮詢話來就來」，但認為市民仍要留意、參與，「香港人唔好咁易放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FsQ4gK33hBuzhpZskrttGeTGE3Q=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4A5PV4B6VZFGJLZUQCIJ2B4XWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFsQ4gK33hBuzhpZskrttGeTGE3Q%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4A5PV4B6VZFGJLZUQCIJ2B4XWQ.jpg&h=2935e4b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■從事會計行業的黎先生質疑「真民主派」能否入閘參選。"},{"pid":"14a5da84676ba060fba276adc469ae7719869167","tid":2490757,"uid":127561,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T00:18:03.000Z","msg":"19年: 邊個投白票就係鬼<br />\n21年: 我係白票兵呀hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1222dc8ef100296173244bc2e3e4181fd2ce6913","tid":2490757,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:26:57.000Z","msg":"白票就係最佳既反抗方法"},{"pid":"904cd3c1bb1b7dae2c5dc6bb609c7a962495ebd2","tid":2490757,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:30:05.000Z","msg":"睇唔到#2、#3"},{"pid":"8f1c30f4a40f5525a54dd6b2a09911f92c30ebb4","tid":2490757,"uid":155346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14a5da84676ba060fba276adc469ae7719869167","tid":2490757,"uid":127561,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T00:18:03.000Z","msg":"19年: 邊個投白票就係鬼<br />\n21年: 我係白票兵呀hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi